strings.Value: "Our supplies grow thin. We'll have to go hunting."
"We are running short of rations. We'll have to rely on the hunt."
"That's good! I'm tired of nibbling dry food every day!"
"You can count me out. But I shall stand ready to support you with wisdom and advice."
"It would be so nice to teach your wolf to go hunting alone, and bring meat back to us! We could just sit here, and â€” here comes our lunch!"
"Knock yourself out! Don't forget your bow! Ha, ha, ha, hmm..."
